Sanjay Bhalara

The driving force behind MarWell growth since its establishment in 2000, Mr. Sanjay Bhalara vision and strategic acumen transformed MarWell. A world-renowned expert on renewable energy, Mr. Bhalara believed in creating sustainable businesses and a sustainable world through energy independence and security.

Daksh Bhalara
